*mysql-init-scripts-2.0_pre1-r2 (15 Jan 2011)

  15 Jan 2011; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org>
  -mysql-init-scripts-2.0_pre1-r1.ebuild,
  +mysql-init-scripts-2.0_pre1-r2.ebuild, files/mysql-5.1.53-conf.d:
